# terra-siege tank — formerly stationary turret. Drives toward player.
# Chassis + turret cap + barrel + tip pip. 32 verts.
# Local frame: +Z forward (chassis aims along yaw). c26 chassis +
# c27 cap + c15 barrel + c17 tip.
#
# Note: e.pos sits at TURRET_MOUNT_HEIGHT (1.6) above terrain in the
# game, so the chassis extends both above and below that anchor.
o tank

# Chassis 3.0 × 3.2 × 3.0 centred at origin (matches TURRET_MOUNT_HEIGHT × 2)
v -1.5 -1.6 -1.5
v  1.5 -1.6 -1.5
v  1.5  1.6 -1.5
v -1.5  1.6 -1.5
v -1.5 -1.6  1.5
v  1.5 -1.6  1.5
v  1.5  1.6  1.5
v -1.5  1.6  1.5

# Turret cap 2.4 × 1.2 × 2.4 at (0, 1.8, 0) — sits at BARREL_HEIGHT relative
# (TURRET_BARREL_HEIGHT 3.4 minus chassis-anchor 1.6 = 1.8)
v -1.2  1.2 -1.2
v  1.2  1.2 -1.2
v  1.2  2.4 -1.2
v -1.2  2.4 -1.2
v -1.2  1.2  1.2
v  1.2  1.2  1.2
v  1.2  2.4  1.2
v -1.2  2.4  1.2

# Barrel 0.6 × 0.4 × 0.6 at (0, 1.8, 1.6) — forward of cap along +Z
v -0.3  1.6  1.3
v  0.3  1.6  1.3
v  0.3  2.0  1.3
v -0.3  2.0  1.3
v -0.3  1.6  1.9
v  0.3  1.6  1.9
v  0.3  2.0  1.9
v -0.3  2.0  1.9

# Tip pip 0.35 × 0.35 × 0.35 at (0, 1.8, 2.4) — further forward
v -0.175 1.625 2.225
v  0.175 1.625 2.225
v  0.175 1.975 2.225
v -0.175 1.975 2.225
v -0.175 1.625 2.575
v  0.175 1.625 2.575
v  0.175 1.975 2.575
v -0.175 1.975 2.575

usemtl c26
g chassis
f 1 4 3 2
f 5 6 7 8
f 1 5 8 4
f 2 3 7 6
f 1 2 6 5
f 4 8 7 3

usemtl c27
g cap
f 9 12 11 10
f 13 14 15 16
f 9 13 16 12
f 10 11 15 14
f 9 10 14 13
f 12 16 15 11

usemtl c15
g barrel
f 17 20 19 18
f 21 22 23 24
f 17 21 24 20
f 18 19 23 22
f 17 18 22 21
f 20 24 23 19

usemtl c17
g tip
f 25 28 27 26
f 29 30 31 32
f 25 29 32 28
f 26 27 31 30
f 25 26 30 29
f 28 32 31 27
